{"id":141284,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/连线：利比亚前线摄影图/","date":"2011-03-25T08:00:05Z","modified":"2011-03-25T08:00:05Z","title":"连线：利比亚前线摄影图","content":"<p><p><span>“奥德赛破晓行动”的目的尚不清晰。无论如何，战争爆发至今的头三天已经显露出一些戏剧化的场面。同伊拉克战争和阿富汗战争非常相似，利比亚战争的硝烟将不知何日散尽，下一个战争场景是什么样的？</span> </p>\n<p><b><span>轰炸机归来</span></b> </p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/5546656576_8a3f042fcd_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></span></p>\n<p><span> </span><a name=\"OLE_LINK2\"><span><span>摄影：</span></span></a><span><span><em><span>Flickr/</span></em></span></span><span><span><span>美国非洲司令部</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span><span>随着伊拉克战争“震慑行动”的结束，</span><span>B-2 </span><span>隐形轰炸机也渐渐消失在战场上。但在这次利比亚战争中，</span><span>B-2</span><span>重出江湖，执行此次全面摧毁利比亚雷达、导弹发射场、机场和战地指挥所的任务。如上面照片所示，一架刚刚完成轰炸任务的</span><span>B-2</span><span>从密苏里</span><span>怀特曼空军基地一路奔袭归来。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><b><span>F-16</span></b><b><span>蓄势待发</span></b></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/5546131876_fb58aa2dbd_z-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />\n</p>\n<p><span> </span><span>摄影：</span><a name=\"OLE_LINK1\"><span>美国非洲司令部</span></a></p>\n<p><span> </span><span>在德国</span><span><span>pangdahlem</span></span><span><span>空军基地，</span></span><span><span>第</span></span><span><span>52</span></span><span><span>战斗机联队的飞行员长官正在部署一架</span></span><span><span>F-16</span></span><span><span>执行一次利比亚攻击行动。</span></span><span><span>F-16</span></span><span><span>将连同</span></span><span><span>F-15</span></span><span><span>成为“奥德赛破晓行动”空中战场的主力将士。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><b><span>“</span></b><b><span>战斧</span></b><b><span>”</span></b><b><span>式巡航导弹</span></b></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/5543045267_8b7345096e_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />\n</p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span>摄影：</span><em><span>Flickr/</span></em><span>美国非洲司令部</span></p>\n<p><span> </span><span><span>美国海军导弹驱逐舰</span></span><span><span>Stout</span></span><span><span>号发射了一枚</span></span><span><span>“</span></span><span><span>战斧</span></span><span><span>”</span></span><span><span>式巡航导弹，而这只是战争头三天由盟军舰队和潜艇发出的</span></span><span><span>136</span></span><span><span>颗导弹之一（实际数字可能大于</span></span><span><span>136</span></span><span><span>）。虽然这些巡航导弹的外表看起来还像是“沙漠风暴行动”的遗留物，但是它内部的导航系统却足以使它成为所向披靡的无人驾驶飞行器。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><b><span>夜型飞机待命：奇尔沙治号（美国制造的反潜航母）</span></b></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span><span>录像：</span></span><i><span>DVIDS</span></i><span> </span><span>（暂无显示）</span></p>\n<p><span> </span><span>美国两栖舰队“奇尔沙治”号一直以其提供的人道主义救援而闻名于世。但是在这段录像中，它已经全服待命准备将其直升飞机和鹞式战斗机投入到更为激励的战役之中。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><b><span>各就各位</span></b></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/5545577757_d8e74a7fe6_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />\n</p>\n<p><span> </span><span>摄影</span><span>：</span><em><span>Flickr/</span></em><span>美国非洲司令部</span></p>\n<p><span> </span><span>哪里有战场，哪里就有后援。在这张照片里，来自第</span><span>48</span><span>战斗联队和以匈牙利为基地的重型运输联队的成员们正在待命，随时准备援助本次禁飞任务。不过，可不要弄错，长时间被捆绑在</span><span>C-17</span><span>或</span><span>C-130</span><span>运输飞机上是非常寒冷和难受的。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><b><span>呃，我们没有帮助反叛者</span></b><b><span>&#8230;&#8230;</span></b></p>\n<p><span> <img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/libya_aftermath_f.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></span></p>\n<p><span>摄影：</span><i><span>Anja Niedringhaus/</span></i><span> </span><span>美联社</span></p>\n<p><span> </span><span>来自“奥德赛破晓行动”总指挥</span><span>CarterHam.</span><span>将军的官方言论表示，此次行动的目的并不是帮助叛乱者推翻卡扎菲政权。</span><span> <br />\n</span></p>\n<p><b><span>海上伙伴</span></b></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/110321-n-om642-039.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />\n</p>\n<p><span> </span><span>摄影：美国海军</span></p>\n<p><span> </span><span>利比亚禁飞区不同于上世纪九十年代禁飞区的特征之一是它在海上的大面积禁飞领空。在利比亚的防空阵地上，不仅舰队和潜艇正在发射巡航导弹，盟军舰队也正在扮演准备应对额外任务的联合平台。在这幅照片里，一架来自法国“戴高乐”号航母的</span><span>“海豚”搜救直升机正准备着陆在美国“惠特尼山”号指挥舰上。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><b><span>昂首阔步的机组人员</span></b></p>\n<p><span> <img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/5546131690_8b9c8bc220_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></span></p>\n<p><span>摄影：</span><em><span>Flickr/</span></em><span>美国非洲司令部</span></p>\n<p><span>在用于进行利比亚上空巡逻任务的起降跑道上，你一定不希望你的</span><span>F-16</span><span>碾到任何碎片或污垢。这就是为什么身处</span><span>Spangdahlem</span><span> </span><span>第</span><span>52</span><span>维修大队的机组人员在</span><span>F-16</span><span>起飞之前要仔细巡查路面状况。</span></p>\n<p><span>摄影：</span><em><span>Flickr/</span></em><span>美国非洲司令部</span></p>\n<p><b><span>拉法埃莱喷射机</span></b></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/rafaele.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /> </span></p>\n<p><span>摄影：</span><i><span>Rafaelenews.blogspot.com</span></i><i><span>/hat tip to the </span></i><i><span>DEW Line&#8217;s Stephen Trimble</span></i><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>法国拉法埃莱喷射机的飞行员在完成一次利比亚侦查任务后走下飞机。</span><span> <br />\n</span></p>\n<p><b><span>逃离</span></b></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/libya_border_f.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /> </span></p>\n<p><span>摄影：</span><i><span>Emilio Morenatti/</span></i><i><span>美联社</span></i></p>\n<p><span>这张照片里，来利比亚工作的加纳人穿过西边的国界线进入突尼斯，他们携带的包裹仅仅不过是些衣服和柔软的可以用来睡觉的东西。而他们只是正在迁徙的</span><span>25</span><span>万民工大军中的小小一部分。自从三周前暴动发生，他们就开始相继逃离利比亚。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><b><span>磨枪霍霍</span></b></p>\n<p><span><b><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/5543044691_0fcfee57bc_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</b></span></p>\n<p><span>摄影：</span><span>美国非洲司令部</span></p>\n<p><span>美国奇尔沙治反潜航母上的一个海军成员正在仔细检查装载在即将飞往战场的“骑士鹰”直升机上的机枪。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><b><span>艾季达比耶之战</span></b></p>\n<p><span><img src=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/wp-content/gallery/libya/5488926072_9ff8d8ba24_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /> </span></p>\n<p><span>摄影：</span><i><span>Flickr/</span></i><i><span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/aljazeeraenglish/5488926072/sizes/z/in/set-72157626062666497/\"><span>al-Jazeera</span></a></span></i><span><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/488523556/dongxinet/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://item.feedsky.com/~feedsky/dongxinet/~8172838/488523556/6276617/1/item.html\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/dongxinet/488523556/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/dongxinet/488523556/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n</p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):caonimaaiziyouATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":306,"categories":[20534],"tags":[15481]}